releases.name: v0.2.3
releases.body:
Please check out [CHANGELOG](https://github.com/lindb/lindb/blob/main/CHANGELOG/CHANGELOG-1.0.md) for a full list of changes.
For installation guides, please check out [Quick start](https://lindb.io/guide/get-started.html) .

## What's Changed
* [opt]: join file paths by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/951
* [bug]: fix get diff agg result using diff group by interval by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/954

releases.name: v0.2.2
releases.body:
- Please check out [CHANGELOG](https://github.com/lindb/lindb/blob/main/CHANGELOG/CHANGELOG-1.0.md) for a full list of changes.
- For installation guides, please check out [Quick start](https://lindb.io/guide/get-started.html) .

## What's Changed
* [feat]: support release with a docker image by @Sn0rt in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/927
* [feat]: read config from env by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/929
* [feat]: env add LINDB_ prefix by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/930
* [feat]: support auto fill group by time interval based on query range by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/944
* [feat]: print config value when server startup by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/933
* [opt]: print error message when handle http request failure by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/934
* [enhance]: need to check rollup Interval when memory database refreshing by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/947
* [enhance]: check database's intervals if valid by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/948
* [opt]: add cli tools to docker image by @Sn0rt in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/940
* [bug]: got unexpected result when async load family data by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/942
* [bug]: fix time picker no display last 30 days by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/931
* [bug]: fix cannot rollup data for windows by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/946
* [bug]: fix miss some source family data when rollup job by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/949
* [bug]: cannot create database if storage not exist by @stone1100 in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/936

## New Contributors
* @Sn0rt made their first contribution in https://github.com/lindb/lindb/pull/927
